{"tid":1220521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"處理示威時的交戰規則","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T04:26:05.000Z","uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d05978bc7d37fa0873e7681d6c7f969776f3602","tid":1220521,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/62568978_10157109203696422_6836943252050935808_o_qDtyh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F62568978_10157109203696422_6836943252050935808_o_qDtyh_1200x0.png&h=6cdbaf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多年前英軍軍訓時，教官跟我們說過，處理示威、暴動時有什麼交戰規則 (Rules of Engagement) 。<br />\n<br />\n身穿防暴裝備的軍人，有責任確保所有人 &mdash; 包括示威者 &mdash; 的人身安全。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/64562935_2384431945126684_8570854642169151488_n_wFk3g_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F64562935_2384431945126684_8570854642169151488_n_wFk3g_1200x0.jpg&h=8717e29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者向你粗言穢語？你要當佢發噏風。更不要說主動問候人老母了。以前在北愛爾蘭，如果某軍人被對方 target ，是有機會被暗殺的。<br />\n<br />\n什麼時候用有可能殺死人的武器，例如橡膠子彈等等呢？就是當有示威者做出有機會令人致命的行為。<br />\n<br />\n向軍人投擲雜物？唔計，因為你們已經手持防暴盾，身穿防護裝備。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/64768651_2384432028460009_211811397443518464_o_lj3be_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F64768651_2384432028460009_211811397443518464_o_lj3be_1200x0.jpg&h=fa769a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向軍人投擲燃燒彈？其實都唔計，因為你可以用防暴盾抵擋。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是「會令人致命的行為」？向無法防禦的人，包括倒地的軍人或其他群眾，投擲燃燒彈之類。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>什麼情況可以瞄準示威者頭部開槍（就算「只是」橡膠子彈）？似冇。上法庭，這不論怎麼說，也是 intention to kill 吧？<br />\n<br />\n什麼情況可以用橡膠子彈。射。記。者？哈哈！你 100% 可以準備上軍事法庭，坐監了。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nN 年前在英國 Folkestone 揸過防暴盾、警棍的醫生上<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/處理示威時的交戰規則/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%99%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E6%88%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=b7b0ea8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%99%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E6%88%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%2F&h=907c0c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/處理示威時的交戰規則/</a>"}]}